adb1510f2a561271e85afb3cdd3f72642b","tid":2329674,"uid":25727,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"清今年收爐未 暫時file咗28單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952d965a54f8dfe247076d4dca675f5c772a0207","tid":2329674,"uid":22622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"求教學<br />\n泊街唔阻人果啲都算<br />\n<br />\n有啲真係好撚過份<br />\n逆線衝燈小路直出而家都好多<br />\n係要俾啲教訓佢"},{"pid":"1bde975b9f4e2a2039a78d0c3bbb0dfb2ea5e66b","tid":2329674,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"清，受左咩刺激？<br />\n比人搞？"},{"pid":"765ad370c552402d7dd60584cce2d62d6fd9bdd9","tid":2329674,"uid":10845,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"話說今日去旁聽交通case<br />\n同場有十幾單案件<br />\n全部都係車cam撚投訴<br />\n全部入晒罪。<br />\n有車cam更佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f70e63d4909cf7ea9c89c65f38d5fc87431452e","tid":2329674,"uid":116696,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"952d965a54f8dfe247076d4dca675f5c772a0207","tid":2329674,"uid":22622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"求教學<br />\n泊街唔阻人果啲都算<br />\n<br />\n有啲真係好撚過份<br />\n逆線衝燈小路直出而家都好多<br />\n係要俾啲教訓佢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"泊街個d我唔理啦 抄牌已經係懲罰<br />\n我淨係針對駕駛態度惡劣嘅司機<br />\n<br />\n1823暫時不處理電郵、手機應用程式、電子表格、文字短訊等文字來函，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n所以1823已經係廢左 唯有直接電子報案<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FCCC%2FPolicePublicPage%3Flanguage%3Dch&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28aVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=064c66d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOEkJS9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOEkJS9.png&h=6a44650e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選擇「交通報告」&gt; 「交通投訴」<br />\n填低簡單個人資料之後再填返事件經過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEtqayV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEtqayV.png&h=de89d858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過個系統好垃圾 冇得upload影片<br />\n鍾意嘅話可以整gif upload上去/<br />\nUp條片上YouTube 補條link 就完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/article_multimedia/36463/10_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Farticle_multimedia%2F36463%2F10_n.jpg&h=f67d650e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過幾日有狗會打比你 同你講睇左條片 問你事件經過<br />\n如果確定有違規會問你想警告個司機定告佢<br />\n（警告就冇用嘅 不如就唔好篤灰）<br />\n會講埋告咩罪 通常都係不小心駕駛<br />\n之後會約你去狗屋簽口供同要你燒碟帶上去(好on9)<br />\n基本上佢睇完條片都已經起左份口供草稿<br />\n上狗屋同你confirm返口供簽個名走得 半個鐘左右<br />\n就會出信比車主 問佢認唔認罪 認就交名<br />\n唔認就可能要上庭 要你上去做證人<br />\n不過如果車cam片明顯睇到有犯規 <br />\n有晒證據都冇得唔認 <br />\n最後等收信 會話你知個結果 罰款同扣幾分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n功德圓滿"},{"pid":"ce818599d840242df343ad2fa51aa7575bb5b334","tid":2329674,"uid":116696,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1bde975b9f4e2a2039a78d0c3bbb0dfb2ea5e66b","tid":2329674,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"清，受左咩刺激？<br />\n比人搞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"冇 純粹睇唔過眼d閪司機"},{"pid":"180e455167135a0a250de71b0bef446c33d82cef","tid":2329674,"uid":116696,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765ad370c552402d7dd60584cce2d62d6fd9bdd9","tid":2329674,"uid":10845,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"話說今日去旁聽交通case<br />\n同場有十幾單案件<br />\n全部都係車cam撚投訴<br />\n全部入晒罪。<br />\n有車cam更佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:32:13.000Z","msg":"抵死啦 <img src=\"/as