2020-12-17T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"唔好搞26攝車😭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"喺我面前攝到過哂雙白就唔好意思了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc012c85d8aeec8097cdb30cdb597d678f3a4c6","tid":2329674,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039ac23e9874cd9fc45a10caa98d5631375bb207","tid":2329674,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df7fdadbe48094beeb6e2abcef60e3fa576f6b74","tid":2329674,"uid":118155,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"4f70e63d4909cf7ea9c89c65f38d5fc87431452e","tid":2329674,"uid":116696,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"952d965a54f8dfe247076d4dca675f5c772a0207","tid":2329674,"uid":22622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"求教學<br />\n泊街唔阻人果啲都算<br />\n<br />\n有啲真係好撚過份<br />\n逆線衝燈小路直出而家都好多<br />\n係要俾啲教訓佢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"泊街個d我唔理啦 抄牌已經係懲罰<br />\n我淨係針對駕駛態度惡劣嘅司機<br />\n<br />\n1823暫時不處理電郵、手機應用程式、電子表格、文字短訊等文字來函，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n所以1823已經係廢左 唯有直接電子報案<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FCCC%2FPolicePublicPage%3Flanguage%3Dch&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28aVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=064c66d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/CCC/PolicePublicPage?language=ch</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOEkJS9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOEkJS9.png&h=6a44650e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選擇「交通報告」&gt; 「交通投訴」<br />\n填低簡單個人資料之後再填返事件經過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEtqayV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEtqayV.png&h=de89d858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過個系統好垃圾 冇得upload影片<br />\n鍾意嘅話可以整gif upload上去/<br />\nUp條片上YouTube 補條link 就完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/tmp_images/article_multimedia/36463/10_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Ftmp_images%2Farticle_multimedia%2F36463%2F10_n.jpg&h=f67d650e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過幾日有狗會打比你 同你講睇左條片 問你事件經過<br />\n如果確定有違規會問你想警告個司機定告佢<br />\n（警告就冇用嘅 不如就唔好篤灰）<br />\n會講埋告咩罪 通常都係不小心駕駛<br />\n之後會約你去狗屋簽口供同要你燒碟帶上去(好on9)<br />\n基本上佢睇完條片都已經起左份口供草稿<br />\n上狗屋同你confirm返口供簽個名走得 半個鐘左右<br />\n就會出信比車主 問佢認唔認罪 認就交名<br />\n唔認就可能要上庭 要你上去做證人<br />\n不過如果車cam片明顯睇到有犯規 <br />\n有晒證據都冇得唔認 <br />\n最後等收信 會話你知個結果 罰款同扣幾分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n功德圓滿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"好嘢係要大大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成鳩日cut雙白 讓線又睇都唔撚睇就出果d撚樣<br />\n個個大地任我行咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆佢個街香港咁多交通意外唔多唔少就係哩d閪司機造成<br />\n<br />\n好彩hi花撞凹都仲話破財擋災<br />\n唔好彩撞著d早排個寶馬閪司機衝燈撞鳩死人<br />\n命仔又無 頭家又散埋 真係多得d閪司機唔少<br />\n<br />\n閪司機沒有一個是無辜的<br />\n見一個舉報一個就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3369606a44335098611ad89ae4e345bf4fed1bd","tid":2329674,"uid":16367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4f70e63d4909cf7ea9c89c65f38d5fc87431452e","tid":2329674,"uid":116696,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"952d965a54f8dfe247076d4dca675f5c772a0207","tid":2329674,"uid":22622,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"求教學<br />\n泊街唔阻人果啲都算<br />\n<br />\n有啲真係好撚過份<br />\n逆線衝燈小路直出而家都好多<br />\n係要俾啲教訓佢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"泊街個d我唔理啦 抄牌已經係懲罰<br />\